name: 'Karakter #17'
description: Karakter #17 is a digital collage. A gif animation arising from toxic smoke. The addiction which creation brings with it. The Zen-Feeling appealing to me. Emperor of Gan. Breeding Art. Thank you. Burning Blond. Smoking Hand. Too much fingers. Yes, Please.
